<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَفَرَأَيْتُمُ الْماءَ الَّذِي تَشْرَبُونَ <span class="c2">(٦٨)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَأَنْتُمْ أَنْزَلْتُمُوهُ مِنَ الْمُزْنِ أَمْ نَحْنُ الْمُنْزِلُونَ <span class="c2">(٦٩)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَوْ نَشاءُ جَعَلْناهُ أُجاجاً فَلَوْلا تَشْكُرُونَ <span class="c2">(٧٠)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَفَرَأَيْتُمُ النَّارَ الَّتِي تُورُونَ <span class="c2">(٧١)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَأَنْتُمْ أَنْشَأْتُمْ شَجَرَتَها أَمْ نَحْنُ الْمُنْشِؤُنَ <span class="c2">(٧٢)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>نَحْنُ جَعَلْناها تَذْكِرَةً وَمَتاعاً لِلْمُقْوِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٣)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَسَبِّحْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الْعَظِيمِ <span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٣٤- أَفَلا يَنْظُرُونَ إِلَى الْإِبِلِ كَيْفَ خُلِقَتْ <span class="c2">(١٧)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَإِلَى السَّماءِ كَيْفَ رُفِعَتْ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَإِلَى الْجِبالِ كَيْفَ نُصِبَتْ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَإِلَى الْأَرْضِ كَيْفَ سُطِحَتْ <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَذَكِّرْ إِنَّما أَنْتَ مُذَكِّرٌ <span class="c2">(٢١)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) الواقعة: ٥٨- ٧٤ مكية<br>(٢) الغاشية: ١٧- ٢١ مكية</p> </div>